title: Tig Notaro: A Joke about Being Misgendered
description: Tig Notaro jokes about being misgendered in her Netflix special, "Happy to Be Here". Grab your tickets at NetflixIsAJokeFest.com to see Tig  and your other favorite comedians in the Netflix is a Joke Fest happening April 28th-May 8th in Los Angeles.
